name: Whitecat (Sadfyr)
description:
The fate of humanity is in your hands. Will you be able to reach Earth in time?

  • The worst arcade ship game you will ever play.
  • A plot that even a two-year-old would write better.
  • The music is good, but because it's made by another guy.
  • Translated with Google Translate.

YouTube channel of the musician.
